<view class="container">
  <view class="page-header">
    <view class="page-title-group">
      <text class="page-title">为家人找到的可能性</text>
      <text class="page-subtitle">围绕您上传的病历，为家人找到可能适合的临床试验 —— 每一项都说清楚为什么。</text>
    </view>
    <view class="filter-btn" bindtap="loadMatches">
      <text>刷新</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="match-stats">
    <view class="stat-item">
      <text class="stat-value">{{matches.length}}</text>
      <text class="stat-label">找到的可能性</text>
    </view>
    <view class="stat-item">
      <text class="stat-value">{{highMatches}}</text>
      <text class="stat-label">高度匹配</text>
    </view>
    <view class="stat-item">
      <text class="stat-value">{{readyMatches}}</text>
      <text class="stat-label">值得优先看</text>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="score-rule-tip">
    <text>我们先展示最匹配的几项 · 数量少会自动放宽标准让您多几个选择。</text>
  </view>

  <view class="score-fallback-tip" wx:if="{{lowScoreMode}}">
    <text>暂时没有高度匹配的结果 —— 我们放宽了标准，下面是还值得一看的候选。</text>
  </view>

  <view class="processing-banner" wx:if="{{activeParseTask}}">
    <view class="processing-banner-head">
      <text class="processing-banner-title">病历还在帮您看懂中</text>
      <text class="processing-banner-progress">{{activeParseTask.progress}}%</text>
    </view>
    <text class="processing-banner-text">{{activeParseTask.text}}</text>
    <view class="processing-banner-bar">
      <view class="processing-banner-fill" style="width: {{activeParseTask.progress}}%;"></view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="supplement-tip" wx:if="{{!loading && needSupplement > 0}}">
    <text class="supplement-text">再补一点病历信息，{{needSupplement}} 个试验会评得更准。</text>
    <button class="supplement-btn" bindtap="goToUpload">去补一补</button>
  </view>

  <view class="fallback-tip" wx:if="{{usingFallback}}">
    <text>{{fallbackMessage || '先给您看一个参考版本，正式结果马上就好'}}</text>
  </view>

  <view class="loading" wx:if="{{loading}}">
    <text>正在为家人找合适的试验…</text>
  </view>

  <view class="empty-state" wx:if="{{!loading && errorMessage}}">
    <text>{{errorMessage}}</text>
  </view>

  <view class="matches-list" wx:if="{{!loading && !errorMessage && matches.length > 0}}">
    <view class="match-card" wx:for="{{matches}}" wx:key="id">
      <!-- U4：人话理由 —— 置顶一行解释「为什么这个研究适合」，不取代下面的 score / decisionHint。 -->
      <view class="human-reason">✓ 为什么适合：{{item.humanReason}}</view>
      <view class="match-card-header" bindtap="toggleMatchExpand" data-id="{{item.id}}">
        <view class="match-content">
          <text class="match-title">{{item.name}}</text>
        </view>
        <view class="match-header-right">
          <view class="match-score-badge">
            <text class="score">{{item.score}}%</text>
            <text class="label">匹配度</text>
          </view>
          <text class="match-expand-indicator">{{item.expanded ? '收起' : '看详情'}}</text>
        </view>
      </view>

      <view class="match-card-summary">
        <view class="match-tags">
          <text class="tag tag-level level-{{item.score >= 80 ? 'high' : (item.score >= 60 ? 'mid' : 'low')}}">{{item.matchLevel}}</text>
          <text class="tag tag-primary">{{item.phase}}</text>
          <text class="tag tag-warning">{{item.type}}</text>
        </view>
        <text class="match-indication">{{item.indication}}</text>
      </view>

      <view wx:if="{{item.expanded}}" class="match-card-expanded">
        <view class="decision-banner tone-{{item.decisionTone}}">
          <text class="decision-label">我们的看法</text>
          <text class="decision-text">{{item.decisionHint}}</text>
        </view>

        <view class="detail-panel">
          <text class="detail-panel-title">分中心</text>
          <view class="sub-center-list" wx:if="{{item.subCenters.length > 0}}">
            <text class="sub-center-chip" wx:for="{{item.subCenters}}" wx:for-item="center" wx:key="index">{{center}}</text>
          </view>
          <view class="column-empty" wx:else>
            <text>分中心信息还没拿到，我们会继续跟进</text>
          </view>
        </view>

        <view class="detail-panel">
          <text class="detail-panel-title">基础信息</text>
          <text class="match-meta" wx:if="{{item.institution}}">研究机构：{{item.institution}}</text>
          <text class="match-meta" wx:if="{{item.nctId}}">试验编号：{{item.nctId}}</text>
          <text class="match-meta" wx:if="{{item.status}}">招募状态：{{item.status}}</text>
        </view>

        <view class="detail-panel" wx:if="{{item.inclusion.length > 0}}">
          <text class="detail-panel-title">入选标准</text>
          <view class="criteria-item inclusion" wx:for="{{item.inclusion}}" wx:for-item="criterion" wx:key="index">
            <text class="criteria-icon">+</text>
            <text class="criteria-text">{{criterion}}</text>
          </view>
        </view>

        <view class="detail-panel" wx:if="{{item.exclusion.length > 0}}">
          <text class="detail-panel-title">排除标准</text>
          <view class="criteria-item exclusion" wx:for="{{item.exclusion}}" wx:for-item="criterion" wx:key="index">
            <text class="criteria-icon">-</text>
            <text class="criteria-text">{{criterion}}</text>
          </view>
        </view>

        <view class="match-actions">
          <button class="btn btn-default" catchtap="viewDetail" data-id="{{item.id}}">看详情</button>
          <button class="btn btn-primary" catchtap="applyTrial" data-id="{{item.id}}">想让研究团队联系我</button>
        </view>
      </view>
    </view>
  </view>

  <view class="empty-state" wx:if="{{!loading && !errorMessage && matches.length === 0}}">
    <text>目前没找到完全贴合的试验 —— 这不代表没有，我们每周更新试验库。</text>
    <button class="btn btn-default mt-30" bindtap="loadMatches">再找一次</button>
  </view>
  <help-fab />
</view>
